title: The People’s Liberation Army of China provides anti-epidemic materials to Belarusian Army in June 2020
description: On June 13, 2020, the People’s Liberation Army of China provided anti-epidemic materials to the armed forces of Belarus. The donated materials included protective suits, medical masks, and other anti epidemic materials.    The monetary value of this donation is unknown.
